title: Tomtom 7 Repack 3 with North_America_720.1803 map
description:
Here goes Tomtom 7 Repack 3 for PPC which includes the latest North America map from Tomtom, this map is very detailed so it&#039;s a lot bigger than the USA_Canadaeh map.

After installing if you have problems with your Bluetooth or sound on your PDA do this to get it working again:
Browse to your Windows directory on your PPC and look for BtCoreIf.dll and BtSdkCE30.dll. Rename them both (for example: "BtCoreIf.old" "BtSdkCE30.old")
then do a soft reset, all better :)

I will only be seeding this for about a day so please download and seed.

All files needed and a readme is included.

Sorry guys, I&#039;m American and I will only be uploading the North America map. I only included one voice, if you want other ones you&#039;ll have to find them yourselves.

This worked great on my HTC Kaiser

Enjoy, if you like it, buy it and support the developers!

-V
